'''Scrumtrelescent''' is a word coined by [[SNL]] comedian [[Will Ferrell]] when doing an impression of '[[The Actors Studio]]' host [[James Lipton]] in order to describe the performance of actor [[Charles Nelson Reilly]] on the [[Match Game]]; used to describe something transcendent and fantastic beyond description